                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/2808" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-0644</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">9193 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">海信“牵手”欧洲杯：是巧合使然还是理所必然？</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Hisense&#39;s sponsoring European Cup: Contigency or Necessity?</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">刘素，陈志军</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">山东财经大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">海信集团</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">电子工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">18 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">国际化战略；体育营销；品牌定位；海外运营；2017百优案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Internationalization strategy;sports marketing;brand positioning;overseas operation</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2016年1月，海信与欧足联正式签约，成为2016年欧洲足球锦标赛（简称欧洲杯）十大顶级赞助商之一。这是欧洲杯设立56年来亮相欧洲杯赛场的首个中国品牌广告。赞助世界顶级体育赛事向来被公认是企业快速提升国际形象的捷径。通过顶级赛事的背书，能够大大缩短全球消费者熟知企业品牌的时间。对于早就提出“大头在外头”的海信而言，大赛事营销更是其加快国际化发展关键的“一步棋”。一直被外界评为“不太会讲故事”的海信，抓住欧足联向中国抛出的橄榄枝，以务实和巧妙的姿态，演绎了一场品牌“走上去”的国际化“撑杆跳”。同时，不菲的赞助费以及虽简单粗暴却行之有效的广告标语在国内外引发了广泛的热议和刷屏，起到了意想不到的宣传效果。
海信欧洲杯营销未来无疑将成为更多中国品牌出海效仿的典范，其背后的成功秘诀和战略逻辑值得更多中国企业深思：为什么欧洲杯这个绝好机会被海信抓住了？企业在什么情况下适合赞助国际顶级赛事？赞助要达到哪些目的？需要解决哪些核心问题？一旦进行了赞助，应该有哪些配套措施来确保权益和效果发挥到最大？如何应对赞助时热闹赞助后冷清对海信运营造成的消极影响？
</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">In January 2016, Hisense signed a formal contract with UEFA to become one of the top ten sponsors of the 2016 European Football Championship (European Cup). It was also the first Chinese brand advertisement for the European Cup in the past 56 years. Sponsoring the world’s top sporting events has always been recognized as a shortcut for companies to rapidly improve their international image, as endorsements through top-level events can significantly reduce the time for global consumers to become familiar with corporate brands. Hisense proposed its “Foreign market priority strategy” many years ago. Now the big sports event marketing is his key to speed up the development of its internationalization strategy. Despite being rated as a poor storyteller, Hisense seized the olive branch throwing from UEFA, in a pragmatic and clever gesture, performed a brand’s international upward “pole jump”. At the same time, the expensive sponsorship fees, although simple but effective advertising slogan sparking widespread debate and scraper in China, played an unexpected effect.
Hisense’s European Cup marketing will undoubtedly become more Chinese brands to follow in the future. The secret of success is worth more Chinese enterprise’s strategic pondering: Why is the great European Cup marketing opportunity caught by Hisense? Under what circumstances are companies suitable for sponsoring international top events? What are the objectives of sponsorship? Once sponsoring, what measures should companies take to ensure that the rights and benefits are maximized? How to cope with the negative impact of sponsorship on Hisense’s operation after the lively sponsorship?
</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2016</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《国际企业管理》、《国际市场营销》、《战略管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">国际企业管理、国际市场营销、企业战略</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2017-08</td>
